    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Distant Trails is a single-player third-person adventure mystery following a group of trail runners on their travels. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194960/extras/cf066215f1d9802b4876ff406699b0f1.poster.avif?t=1770142513\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194960/extras/cf066215f1d9802b4876ff406699b0f1.webm?t=1770142513\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194960/extras/cf066215f1d9802b4876ff406699b0f1.mp4?t=1770142513\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Protect the big outdoors:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A quiet getaway to a remote island to get back to nature and run some trails is about to take a twist into the unexpected.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take your trail runners on an adventure through the varied landscape negotiating the terrain and managing your supplies. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Work as a team to uncover the truth about what is happening on the island.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194960/extras/d2065cab00e457b5644b5f5fe50c8802.poster.avif?t=1770142513\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194960/extras/d2065cab00e457b5644b5f5fe50c8802.webm?t=1770142513\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194960/extras/d2065cab00e457b5644b5f5fe50c8802.mp4?t=1770142513\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A beautiful muddy open world filled with story driven missions and running challenges.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Designed by a trail runner to have real world trail running problems to deal with like injury, fuelling and getting enough sleep.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Physical running simulation with varying hill gradients and ground surfaces all affecting speed and foot grip.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Resource management of supplies on the trail with limited space in backpacks.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Control multiple characters with different running strengths to switch between and work together as a team.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Continuous save system allows exiting the game at any time and resuming later or quick reloading if need to undo an action.</p></li></ul>",
